<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ،<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٥١٢⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١٦٠٩٢ -<span class="c5"> عَنْ جَعْفَرٍ قَالَ:</span> سَمِعْتُ يَزِيدَ الرَّقَاشِيَّ، عَنِ الْحَسَنِ،<span class="c5"> أَنَّهُ قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«إِزَارٌ وَرِدَاءٌ ظَهْرَانِيٌّ مُعَقَّدَةٌ»</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«ثِيَابٌ يُؤْتَى بِهَا مِنَ الْبَحْرَيْنِ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>